<D>__{they can't see, but they have killer sonar. they'll attack anything that moves or makes a sound. even if you get past them, you'd be dead before you covered a hundred yards. if the terminators don't get you, the fallout will heavy rads all the way to the gulf coast, nothing can live there.}
